### HeyGen API — REST Client test file
### Cài extension: humao.rest-client
### Cách dùng: click "Send Request" phía trên mỗi block `###`
### API key lấy ở https://app.heygen.com/settings → API

@apiKey = {{$dotenv HEYGEN_API_KEY}}
@baseUrl = https://api.heygen.com
@uploadUrl = https://upload.heygen.com


### ============================================================
### USER & ACCOUNT
### ============================================================

### Get current user / remaining credits
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/user/remaining_quota
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ============================================================
### AVATARS
### ============================================================

### List avatar looks (avatars + talking photos)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/avatars
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### List avatar groups
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/avatar_group.list
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Get avatar group detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/avatar_group/REPLACE_GROUP_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Get avatar look detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/avatar/REPLACE_AVATAR_ID/details
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Update avatar look (rename)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v2/avatars/REPLACE_AVATAR_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New avatar name"
}


### Create photo avatar
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/photo_avatar/photo/generate
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Photo Avatar",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/portrait.jpg"
}


### Create prompt avatar (AI generated from prompt)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/photo_avatar/photo/generate
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Prompt Avatar",
  "prompt": "A confident 30yo asian woman in business suit, studio lighting",
  "age": "Young Adult",
  "gender": "Woman",
  "ethnicity": "Asian American"
}


### Create digital twin (from video footage)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/video.create_avatar
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Digital Twin",
  "video_url": "https://example.com/footage.mp4"
}


### Create avatar consent (cho private avatar)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/avatar_group/REPLACE_GROUP_ID/consent
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reroute_url": "https://example.com/consent-done"
}


### ============================================================
### VOICES
### ============================================================

### List voices (public library)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/voices
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### List private/cloned voices
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/voices?type=private
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Design voice (AI tạo voice từ prompt)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/voice/design
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Warm, confident female narrator, middle-aged",
  "gender": "female",
  "locale": "en-US",
  "seed": 0
}


### ============================================================
### TEXT-TO-SPEECH
### ============================================================

### Create speech (TTS)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/audio.generate
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "voice_id": "2d5b0e6cf36f460aa7fc47e3eee4ba54",
  "input_text": "Xin chào các bạn, đây là giọng đọc thử.",
  "input_type": "text",
  "speed": 1.0,
  "pitch": 0
}


### ============================================================
### VIDEO GENERATION
### ============================================================

### Create video from avatar (text → video)
# @name createVideoFromAvatar
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/video/generate
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_inputs": [
    {
      "character": {
        "type": "avatar",
        "avatar_id": "Daisy-inskirt-20220818",
        "avatar_style": "normal"
      },
      "voice": {
        "type": "text",
        "input_text": "Xin chào, đây là video test từ HeyGen API.",
        "voice_id": "2d5b0e6cf36f460aa7fc47e3eee4ba54"
      }
    }
  ],
  "dimension": { "width": 1280, "height": 720 }
}


### Create video từ talking photo / photo avatar
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/video/generate
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_inputs": [
    {
      "character": {
        "type": "talking_photo",
        "talking_photo_id": "REPLACE_TALKING_PHOTO_ID"
      },
      "voice": {
        "type": "text",
        "input_text": "Nội dung demo cho talking photo.",
        "voice_id": "2d5b0e6cf36f460aa7fc47e3eee4ba54"
      }
    }
  ],
  "dimension": { "width": 1080, "height": 1920 }
}


### Create video từ image (animate ảnh)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/video/generate
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_inputs": [
    {
      "character": {
        "type": "talking_photo",
        "talking_photo_id": "REPLACE_IMAGE_ID"
      },
      "voice": {
        "type": "audio",
        "audio_url": "https://example.com/voiceover.mp3"
      }
    }
  ],
  "dimension": { "width": 1920, "height": 1080 }
}


### ============================================================
### VIDEO MANAGEMENT
### ============================================================

### List videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/video.list?limit=20
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### List videos — pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/video.list?limit=20&token=REPLACE_TOKEN
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### List videos — filter by title
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/video.list?limit=20&title=REPLACE_SUBSTRING
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Get video status
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/video_status.get?video_id=REPLACE_VIDEO_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Delete video
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/video.delete?video_id=REPLACE_VIDEO_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ============================================================
### VIDEO TRANSLATION
### ============================================================

### List supported translation languages
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/video_translate/target_languages
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Create video translation
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/video_translate
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_url": "https://example.com/source.mp4",
  "output_language": "Vietnamese",
  "title": "Test translation",
  "speaker_num": 1
}


### List translations
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/video_translate/list?limit=10
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Get translation status
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/video_translate/REPLACE_TRANSLATION_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Update translation title
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v2/video_translate/REPLACE_TRANSLATION_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "title": "New title" }


### Delete translation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v2/video_translate/REPLACE_TRANSLATION_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ============================================================
### LIPSYNC
### ============================================================

### Create lipsync (thay audio + sync môi)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/video/lipsync
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "video_url": "https://example.com/source.mp4",
  "audio_url": "https://example.com/new-audio.mp3",
  "title": "Lipsync test",
  "mode": "speed"
}


### List lipsync jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/video/lipsync/list?limit=10
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Get lipsync status
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/video/lipsync/REPLACE_LIPSYNC_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Update lipsync title
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v2/video/lipsync/REPLACE_LIPSYNC_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "title": "New title" }


### Delete lipsync
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v2/video/lipsync/REPLACE_LIPSYNC_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ============================================================
### VIDEO AGENT (one-shot AI video generation)
### ============================================================

### Create video agent session (chat mode — recommended)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v3/video-agents/sessions
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Tạo video giới thiệu về AI Agent cho người Việt, giọng nam, 60 giây",
  "mode": "chat",
  "orientation": "portrait"
}


### Create video agent session (generate mode — fire-and-forget)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v3/video-agents/sessions
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Video ngắn giới thiệu khóa học AI Agent",
  "mode": "generate"
}


### Get video agent session
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/video-agents/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Send message to video agent session
POST {{baseUrl}}/v3/video-agents/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/messages
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Chọn voice số 2 và dùng style kinh doanh"
}


### Stop video agent session
POST {{baseUrl}}/v3/video-agents/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/stop
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### List videos produced in a session
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/video-agents/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/videos
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### Get session resource
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/video-agents/sessions/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/resources/REPLACE_RESOURCE_ID
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### List video agent styles
GET {{baseUrl}}/v3/video-agents/styles
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ============================================================
### ASSET UPLOAD
### ============================================================

### Upload asset (raw binary) — Content-Type theo file:
###   image/jpeg | image/png | video/mp4 | audio/mpeg
POST {{uploadUrl}}/v1/asset
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/your/file.jpg
